 Website https://www.ablemuse.com Type Of Publisher Magazine, Online, Press Genres Published Creative Nonfiction, Fiction, Poetry, Cross Genre Hybrid, Audio, Autobiography Memoir, Criticism Reviews, Environment Nature, Essays, Experimental, Humor, Interviews, Mystery Crime, Reviews, Translation, Visual Art Year Established 1999 Address San Jose, California Name Alexander S Pepple Title Editor & Publisher Email [email protected] Mission Statement / Editorial Focus Able Muse is an independent literary journal (founded in 1999) devoted to publishing masterfully crafted writing and fostering a serious community of readers and writers. We feature poetry—with a special emphasis on metrical and formal verse in a contemporary idiom and exceptional free verse—alongside translation, fiction, creative nonfiction, essays, interviews, reviews, and visual art. Our editorial focus is on work that marries technical skill with imaginative force: language that is precise and memorable, musicality without mannerism, and forms—traditional or innovative—used with purpose and freshness.  Able Muse’s mission extends beyond the journal through a family of related presses and platforms: Able Muse Press (https://www.ablemusepress.com
), Word Galaxy Press (https://www.wordgalaxy.com
), and Many Words Press (https://www.manywords.com
), which publish poetry, fiction, and anthologies by emerging and established writers. We also host Eratosphere (https://www.ablemuse.com/erato
), our long-running online literary workshop and discussion forum dedicated to craft, revision, and literary conversation. Together, these efforts support a culture of attentive reading, rigorous standards, and enduring literary exchange. Accepts Unsolicited Submissions Yes Submission Guidelines URL https://www.ablemuse.com/submit Reading Period Year round Charges Writers A Submission/Reading Fee no Author Payments royalties, copies Formats paperback, hardcover, ebook, audio, video, print, digital Contests no Facebook https://www.facebook.com/groups/22503883607 Twitter https://x.com/ablemuse Instagram https://www.instagram.com/ablemusepress/ Average Unique Visitors Per Month 8,000 How Frequently Is Content Updated? Quarterly Number Of Issues Per Year 1 Price Per Issue $23.95 Subscription Price $19.00 Total Subscribers 250 Total Circulation 500 Number Of Books Published Per Year 8 Distributors Ingram
